## Third-Party Licenses

This project uses the following open-source data sources and libraries:

### Data Sources (API)
- **Open-Meteo** — Free weather & air-quality API
  - License: Creative Commons Attribution 4.0
  - URL: https://open-meteo.com/
- **Seoul Open Data (서울 열린데이터광장)** — Public bike-share data
  - License: Public data (국가공공데이터)
  - URL: https://data.seoul.go.kr/
- **Nager.Date** — Public holidays API
  - License: Free for non-commercial
  - URL: https://date.nager.at/
- **OpenStreetMap Nominatim** — Geocoding
  - License: ODbL
  - URL: https://nominatim.openstreetmap.org/

### Frameworks (planned)
- **Toss Granite** — Apache 2.0
- **TDS (Toss Design System)** — Proprietary (Toss)
- **react-native-gifted-charts** — MIT (TBD)

